        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm rounded-3 p-2 holo-c">
          <h3 class="card-title h4">Initial Assessment (90 minutes)</h3>
          <p class="card-text">Our comprehensive initial assessment includes:</p>
          <ul>
            <li class="card-text">Full assessment of symptoms and medical history</li>
            <li class="card-text">Discussion of pessary indications and contraindications</li>
            <li class="card-text">Physical examination of posture and movement patterns</li>
            <li class="card-text">Breathing and abdominal examination</li>
            <li class="card-text">Vaginal pelvic floor assessment</li>
            <li class="card-text">Prolapse measurement with a speculum</li>
            <li class="card-text">Selection and fitting of appropriate pessary</li>
            <li class="card-text">Trial period with comfort check</li>
            <li class="card-text">Self-management instruction</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="card-text">This thorough assessment ensures we understand your specific condition and needs, allowing us to provide the most effective treatment plan. Sharon's extensive experience means you'll receive expert care throughout the process.</p>
