          <p class="card-text">After your initial fitting, we provide a structured follow-up care schedule:</p>
          <ul>
            <li class="card-text">2-week initial follow-up to ensure proper fit and comfort</li>
            <li class="card-text">3-month check-up to assess effectiveness and make adjustments if needed</li>
            <li class="card-text">6-month assessment to monitor progress and tissue health</li>
            <li class="card-text">12-month review for long-term management</li>
          </ul>
